  m_text: 'Nusantara Battle is an Indonesian cultural game featuring a variety of
    exciting mini-games in both Single-Player and Multiplayer modes. Developed to
    introduce the rich culture of Indonesia, it revives the thrill and joy of its
    traditional games.


    Win every match, defeat your opponents, and prove your
    skills in the ultimate traditional Indonesian gaming experience!'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
